ZH: 我姐姐是一名裁缝。
EN: My sister is a tailor.
ZH: 这家裁缝店的技术很好。
EN: The tailoring skills of this shop are very good.
ZH: 他去见了一位裁缝，为了定制一套西装。
EN: He went to see a tailor to have a suit custom-made.
ZH: 这件衣服裁缝做得太大了。
EN: The tailor made this garment too big.
ZH: 裁缝刚开始学习如何缝制衣物。
EN: The tailor has just started learning how to sew clothes.
ZH: 她母亲是一位有名的裁缝师。
EN: Her mother is a well-known dressmaker.
ZH: 我需要找一位好的裁缝帮我改裤子的长度。
EN: I need to find a good tailor to help me alter the length of my pants.
ZH: 在很多农村地区，人们还将衣物带给裁缝修补。
EN: In many rural areas, people still take their clothes to tailors for repairs.
ZH: 这个裁缝可以按照我的要求做一套正式的礼服。
EN: This tailor can make a formal suit according to my requirements.
ZH: 我妈妈是一位退休的裁缝师，她曾经制作过很多漂亮的衣服。
EN: My mom is a retired tailor, and she has made many beautiful clothes.
ZH: 这位裁缝经验丰富，可以做各种不同的款式。
EN: This tailor is experienced and can make different styles.
ZH: 裁缝店里有很多各式各样的面料可供选择。
EN: There are many different fabrics to choose from in the tailor shop.
ZH: 我找到了一个裁缝帮我重做这件旧西装。
EN: I found a tailor to remake this old suit for me.
ZH: 这件衣服上的钮扣松了，我应该找个裁缝补一下。
EN: The buttons on this garment are loose, I should find a tailor to fix them.
ZH: 我奶奶以前是村里的唯一一位裁缝，她非常有名。
EN: My grandmother used to be the only tailor in the village, and she was very famous.
ZH: 这家裁缝店可以根据客户的要求量身定制制服。
EN: This tailor shop can customize uniforms according to customers' requirements.
ZH: 裁缝师傅在裙子上绣了一朵花，非常精致。
EN: The tailor embroidered a flower on the skirt, which looks very delicate.
ZH: 这位裁缝每天都需要用尺子测量客人的尺寸。
EN: The tailor needs to measure the size of customers with a ruler every day.
ZH: 我按照裁缝的建议选择了一种合适的面料。
EN: I chose a suitable fabric based on the tailor's suggestion.
ZH: 这位裁缝非常认真，每个细节都处理得很好。
EN: This tailor is very meticulous, and every detail is handled well.
